"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"2021\\\\.12.27\\n\\n本以为老外都去过圣诞，市场会一片冷清，没想到整个市场的情绪却逐渐稳定，底部逐渐稳固，利空消去，随着主流公链和老牌DEFI的活跃，元宇宙龙头回归，市场趁比特币即将突破之际赛道方向已图穷匕见，亮剑在即，就等总司令一声令下，Web3.0依然是我非常推荐且重点布局的赛道，这里面ENS是你必须关注的币种，匿名币ZEC、ZEN会是各国政府对数字货币交易征税政策发布的一个避税利器，你不得不关注这个细分，市场遍地黄金，这个时候，该是你放大一些风险，拣货的时候了，一季度，回头看，你会觉得自己当时的地板有多低，让我们一起期待行情的到来！\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/KRzdolub-JKsJr6ssEGi7.png?height=627&width=1120)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640612253,\"title\":\"市场情绪逐渐稳定，比特币需要一根放量绿柱点燃市场！\"},\"digest\":\"gX8dtYBVYSXpApGntw_kKBtm1LKFlhRsZZHTgUFHps4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9B2df5F5098Dc1DD8119a51280a73Cfd3d029155\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ahve0D1lhev53_UsL-gm7KUlODaBLOwGBDZK1rF_1J8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eLAg3Zww0GMGwVJSFlPXlmsoaRJxisj6zK26wIm_-dc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"HsE5hsThNpsOfBhaeigIQ1yjcCuXQR-kYJAurusTDXfZW-NLagoBN-B9Y3yK2KfQlPBOXdgH5YOuUqKtxncG0Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xed6ce7fb2276d0fca9197c3d39a4dbd2e58e24964c4f942eaa9fbf3882ad26d46dff1ef690eb30c1b0b8b681ad371af4d150f2f8430c7f87f38cd3a3cd8fab281b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ahve0D1lhev53_UsL-gm7KUlODaBLOwGBDZK1rF_1J8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eLAg3Zww0GMGwVJSFlPXlmsoaRJxisj6zK26wIm_-dc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"gX8dtYBVYSXpApGntw_kKBtm1LKFlhRsZZHTgUFHps4\"}"